    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "his project aims to support Nepal in achieving the SDGs and the targets of 15th plan by creating enabling environment and capacity development through accelerated implementation. Inclusion is an integral part of this initiative as is the integration of poverty, environmental management and climate change: the new sustainable development agenda reflects a greater recognition of challenges arising from depleted natural capital, climate vulnerability, gender inequality, rural-urban migration and rising resource demands, all of which disproportionately affect the livelihoods and well-being of the poor and vulnerable. The project hence will mainstream gender and social inclusion throughout the project interventions."
      },
